data.description: Conveniently located condominium in the highly sought-after Highgrove Gardens gated community. Enjoy exceptionally designed one level living with your grand bedroom, laundry, garage and living spaces all on the main floor. This home is perfect for casual entertaining, with an open floor plan connecting the the living area, kitchen and sunroom or more formal entertaining in the separate dining room. Upstairs are TWO additional ensuite bedrooms with walk-in closets and full bathrooms.The upgrades and special features include plantation shutters that are carried throughout the house, driveway pavers, built in shelving in the garage and extended back patio with covered seating area.The HOA fee includes Trash, Recycle, Landscaping and Rural Metro.This home in located in the back of the neighborhood and has a peaceful backyard.
